title: 80. Taking Your Power Back- Codependency Edition
description:
Hey sis!

In this episode, we are talking all about filling YOUR cup. Have you been feeling like you have been there for EVERY single person except... you? Have you been feeling like you're carrying a heavy load of showing up for others and feeling jaded and down about your own well-being? Listen to THIS. You won't want to miss it!

Click here to get your FREE copy of my Anatomy of Self Love workbook
